
HOW TO PRODUCE EXAMPLES
=======================

A. The directory including the intlist library et other C examples is c.

All examples compile for

        CPP=$CPP" -I $FRAMAC/libc"



B. Before lauching CELIA, please ensure that you have set:

B.1. the CINV and LD_LIBRARY_PATH environment variable as 
     shown in $CINV/install.sh

B.2. the parameters of the analysis in a .prop file. Examples
     of .prop files are given in this directory and in the directories
     ref/intlist*/*/

B.3. the C files use the intlist.h library.


C. Call CELIA by executing

	frama-c-Celia.byte -celia -celia-cinv-opt opt.prop <input c files>


